{"tid":2162483,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"而家d私家診所係咪要幫政府跑數驗武肺？","createTime":"2020-08-18T06:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T16:49:01.000Z","uid":59985,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"869d7657fda087c4e010ca8b7ffe295a400c0fcc","tid":2162483,"uid":59985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>去睇私家睇普通病嘅人留意番</strong><br />\n<span class=\"red\">而家唔知係咪d診所要跑數叫人驗<br />\n佢地有d醫生會講到強制要去驗咁嘅</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n===============================<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，話說我上星期有睇過醫生，有d喉嚨痛未清冇咳就走去睇醫生，個醫生係私家醫生，但係係d綜合醫療嗰d。<br />\n<br />\n我一入去留意到正常睇醫生佢係開張白色單寫，<br />\n但一入去佢係開張粉紅色。<br />\n佢就問我因咩事黎睇醫生，我話喉嚨痛。<br />\n我講埋有冇痰啊，或者有冇咳之類嗰d喇<br />\n<br />\n咁之後古怪嘅野就黎喇，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：佢話比兩個樽我去驗口水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我就話下咩一定要驗？<br />\n因為我上星期黎睇冇話要驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢就話：你而家上呼吸道感染，因為唔知有冇肺炎，咁驗下好d。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就話：你呢個係政府架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢就話：er 係啊政府嗰個<br />\n佢繼續講：你唔驗冇得番工架而家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我：下，有得咁架咩？我番左喇而家。邊有話人一定要驗，即係我唔驗而家唔番得去公司？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢：啊 係啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我：我出去私家驗唔得架咩？我唔想驗政府wor。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢就開始拋我：er. 私家好似要驗3千wor<br />\n我心諗明明之前上網睇千幾就有🙄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我：下咁我唔驗，總之我唔會驗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢：我而家寫幾日假比你喇，但係我會寫明你呢幾日病假係未驗肺炎嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我：哦 咁你寫lo (我唔知佢係咪覺得好多人想要佢嗰幾日假，其實我冇諗過要放假，我真係淨係得喉嚨痛，其他咩都冇)<br />\n<br />\n之後講完出左去<br />\n我同個登記護士講你個醫生好古怪wor<br />\n佢講到唔驗肺炎唔可以得番工咁<br />\n佢係講到一定要驗lo<br />\n個護士就話可能而家高峰期<br />\n咁其實就冇話強制要驗嘅<br />\n<br />\n我話唔係wor，<br />\n佢頭先明明唔係咁講講到一定要驗咁<br />\n佢就話我一係再問下醫生<br />\n咁之後佢都係好似之前咁解釋喇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">唔知而家d醫生係咪要交數<br />\n如果大家有咩事睇醫生要去攞樽仔<br />\n大家就小心d喇<br />\n其實私家攞樽仔好多都係比番政府驗<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好貪嗰幾日假就聽個醫生講<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實冇咩病徵大家就唔好驗<br />\n而家驗好大機會會攞左d DNA送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得有少少病徵<br />\n可以試下深呼吸，然後閉氣一陣先呼氣，<br />\n睇下會唔會咳/ 好唔暢順<br />\n咁樣可以簡單睇到肺個情況<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">唔好比個醫生講幾句就去驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住你有自由唔驗的<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有病徵又真係想驗去私家先啊唔該<br />\n下面附番化驗嘅list<br />\n：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1824535/即時-港聞-病毒檢測-醫療機構及私家醫院檢測一覽-最平-250起\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1824535%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E5%8F%8A%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD-%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%B3-250%E8%B5%B7&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkFz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=e9210dda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1824535%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E5%8F%8A%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD-%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%B3-250%E8%B5%B7&h=6e6bdd1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1824535/即時-港聞-病毒檢測-醫療機構及私家醫院檢測一覽-最平-250起</a>"},{"pid":"bfa826913cadb149093e8a3acba3a26641532f4c","tid":2162483,"uid":59985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"自推十次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851920e2eb5019011a1c14999ca8b382c66cce36","tid":2162483,"uid":7662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪藍醫生自願幫國家跑數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係唔好貪果幾日病假，一個唔小心比人DNA送中就hihi<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87465c6eb50dd18dda687a35b2368e3db24ef8e8","tid":2162483,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"俾錢私家好過"},{"pid":"9bb7362ee2cada8448510cf7043840e2bf4f7450","tid":2162483,"uid":59985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.